snippet.title: Best VGM 669 - Panzer Dragoon Saga - Sora Mi Areru Ec Sancitu
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2164 - https://youtu.be/qqa_pXXSMDg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega Saturn
Panzer Dragoon Saga (1998)
Sora Mi Areru Ec Sancitu (Ending)
Saori Kobayashi & Mariko Nanba
